    {
      "title": "WARGEAR ABILITIES",
      "entries": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Master Vox: Each time the OFFICER in the bearer\u2019s unit issues an Order , it can issue it to an eligible unit up to 24\" away. Medi-pack: At the start of your Command phase , if the bearer\u2019s unit is below its Starting Strength , you can return up to D3 destroyed PLATOON models (excluding CHARACTERS ) to this unit. Regimental Standard: Add 1 to the Objective Control characteristic of models in the bearer\u2019s unit."
        }
      ]
    },
